<td><span lang="ar" xml:lang="ar">لا أعْرِف</span></td>
<td><span title="DIN 31635 Arabic" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none">lā ʾaʿrif</span></td>
<td><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA">/laː ʔaʕrif/</span></td>
